OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,FSir Chris Hoy has said his "selfless"
OL,7,Fwife Sarra kept her multiple sclerosis
OL,8,F(MS) diagnosis a secret while
OL,9,Fsupporting him through his cancer
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,FSir Chris, 48, one of Britain's most
OL,13,Fsuccessful Olympians, revealed on
OL,14,FOctober 20 that he has terminal
OL,15,Fprostate cancer, having first shared
OL,16,Fhis diagnosis in February.
