OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,FIn an extract from his memoir All That
OL,7,FMatters: My Toughest Race Yet,
OL,8,Fpublished in The Sunday Times, Sir
OL,9,FChris praised Sarra for her unwavering
OL,10,Fsupport while facing "this absolute
OL,11,Fcrisis in the midst of my own".
OL,13,FHe recalled Sarra undergoing a routine
OL,14,FMRI scan just a week after his cancer
OL,15,Fdiagnosis to investigate a tingling
OL,16,Fsensation in her face and tongue.
OL,18,FSarra joked that the scan was her
OL,19,Fchance "to have a lie down for an
OL,20,Fhour" and was "as close to a spa day
OL,21,Fas she'd get," Sir Chris said.
