OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,FHe added: "Afterwards, she continued
OL,7,Fto support me wholly and completely,
OL,8,Fleading me to push all thoughts of her
OL,9,FMRI scan away, given her symptoms had
OL,10,Flong since disappeared.
OL,12,FAfter the scan, a tearful Sarra,
OL,13,Fstruggling to speak, told Sir Chris
OL,14,Fand their children, Callum and Chloe,
OL,15,Fthat doctors "think it might be
OL,16,Fmultiple sclerosis".
OL,18,FHe said: "I immediately broke down,
OL,19,Fdistraught both by the news and the
OL,20,Ffact she'd received it without me
OL,21,Fthere."
