OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,FSarra had known about the diagnosis a
OL,7,Fmonth before.
OL,9,F"It was so hard to try to compute that
OL,10,Fshe had absorbed the awfulness of this
OL,11,Fdiagnosis alone, without sharing it
OL,12,Fwith me, in order to protect me," Sir
OL,13,FChris explained.
OL,15,F"I tried to let the words sink in as
OL,16,Fmy mind was spinning, trying to
OL,17,Funderstand what had been happening to
OL,18,Fher, all while she had been
OL,19,Faccompanying me to every one of my own
OL,20,Fhospital appointments.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/8
