OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,F"I couldn't believe what I was
OL,7,Fhearing; Sarra, so fit and well, able
OL,8,Fand healthy, was facing this absolute
OL,9,Fcrisis in the midst of my own."
OL,11,FSarra was later told that year that
OL,12,Fher MS was "very active and
OL,13,Faggressive," requiring treatment "very
OL,14,Fquickly".
OL,16,FSir Chris recalled Sarra telling her
OL,17,Fdoctor that her husband had stage 4
OL,18,Fcancer, saying, "I need you to help me
OL,19,Foutrun this."
