OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,F"I couldn't quite fathom the amount of
OL,7,Fstrength she showed to be able to take
OL,8,Fthis news with such fortitude."
OL,10,FSarra began receiving treatment as Sir
OL,11,FChris was finishing his chemotherapy
OL,12,Fin March.
OL,14,FHe said she now receives medication
OL,15,Fvia intravenous drip at hospital
OL,16,Fvisits every six months.
