OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy's 'selfless' wife kept
OL,4,CMS a secret during his cancer treatment
OL,6,FThe six-time Olympic gold medallist
OL,7,Fdescribes Sarra as "the centre of my
OL,8,Flife". The pair have been married
OL,9,Fsince 2010.
OL,11,FIn his book, he said: "Sarra has
OL,12,Famazed me with all that she has faced.
OL,13,FShe has supported me and encourages me
OL,14,Fevery step of the way, but rarely
OL,15,Fspeaks about her own symptoms."
OL,17,FOn Thursday, after her husband's
OL,18,Fannouncement, Sarra said on Instagram
OL,19,Fthat she was "completely overwhelmed"
OL,20,Fby the "kind, thoughtful and helpful
OL,21,Fmessages".
