OL,6,FShe described Sir Hoy as her "real-
OL,7,Flife superhero".
OL,9,FWhat is MS?
OL,11,FMultiple sclerosis is a chronic,
OL,12,Fincurable condition affecting the
OL,13,Fbrain and spinal cord.
OL,15,FMedicines and other treatments can
OL,16,Fhelp manage symptoms that include
OL,17,Fextreme tiredness, vision problems,
OL,18,Fand difficulty walking or balancing.
